Our Promise:
  ∙ Your teleprompter videos and scripts are not collected.
  ∙ We don't collect information that could be linked to your identity.

We Collect the Following data:
  ∙ Anonymous usage data, location, and device identifiers through the use of Mixpanel, a third-party analytics service.
  ∙ Information related to in-app purchases, including lifetime purchases and subscriptions, through the use of Adapty, RevenueCat & Superwall, which are third-party subscription management services.
  ∙ Feedback collected in the 'contact us' section. We use Mailgun to send the emails.

We use the information we collect to:
  ∙ Provide and improve the App's functionality
  ∙ Understand how the App is used and improve its performance
  ∙ Manage in-app purchases and subscriptions
  ∙ Comply with legal obligations

Sharing of Information:
We may share the information we collect with our third-party service providers, including Mixpanel, Adapty, RevenueCat, Superwall, and Mailgun, who assist us in providing and improving the App. Please visit our service providers' individual privacy pages for more information on how they handle data.

Data Retention:
We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide the App's functionality and comply with legal obligations.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the App's privacy practices, please contact us at jordanzeleny@gmail.com.
